            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> If a string, index each value by this field name\n\n+1 we should support this pattern everywhere that we accept a \"predicate\". Wonder how we can operationalize/standardize this...\n\nAnd I see from the TODO in shared.lua that this PR is a followup to our previous discussions. Nice!",
