            "body": "Is `runtime/lua/vim/func/_memoize.lua` undesirable here? \n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/78111e5371f50f42d3999b2e475953d9c8a30c27/runtime/lua/vim/func.lua#L35",
